snippet.title: Girls' Frontline II: Exilium | Gameplay Demo 3 (4K/60FPS Upload)
snippet.description:
"Girls' Frontline II: Exilium" is a "XCOM style" strategy RPG mobile and PC game that is in full 3D with ACG style. The game includes "Gunsmith" style gun customization, Tarkov-like game mode, and more!

Closed Beta Test 3 for the CN servers is confirmed to be on 20 July 2023, and the EN translation is well on its way!
_______________________________________________

GFL2 Website: https://gf2.sunborngame.com/index
